&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: &lt;/strong&gt;Remote (US)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reports to: &lt;/strong&gt;Chief Executive Officer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re building ambitious new product and service offerings at Finite State, and we&#39;re looking for an experienced Director of Product Management who can set the strategic vision for a product area and lead a team to execute against it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a high-impact, high-visibility leadership role for a PM leader who:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has deep domain knowledge in product security or adjacent cybersecurity areas and understands how security practitioners think and buy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excels at synthesizing qualitative and quantitative data to drive sound product decisions across a team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Is fluent in AI tools for research, content generation, and synthesis — and instills those habits across their team to multiply output&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Is as AI native thinker and is excited to help build and lead the industry&#39;s first agentic product security assurance team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own a product area end-to-end — and lead the team doing it.&lt;/strong&gt; Set the vision, define key outcomes and metrics for product and customer success, and guide your team of PMs and cross-functional partners to build the right things at the right time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be the authority on your domain.&lt;/strong&gt; Develop and champion a deep understanding of the product security assurance challenges our customers face, and bring that perspective into executive and go-to-market conversations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive strategic prioritization.&lt;/strong&gt; Make clear, defensible calls on what gets built and what doesn&#39;t — balancing customer needs, market opportunities, and business goals at a portfolio level.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead AI-powered product operations.&lt;/strong&gt; Champion the use of AI automation to ensure the team always has the latest data driving product decisions, and build repeatable workflows your team can scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own product messaging at a strategic level.&lt;/strong&gt; Partner closely with our go-to-market leadership to shape how we position new and improved capabilities — from customer narratives to analyst briefings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build across software and services.&lt;/strong&gt; Our combination of software and services is key to our success. Partner with our services leadership to deliver exceptional outcomes for customers and identify new revenue opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Develop your team.&lt;/strong&gt

